          "* the (acquisiton) funnel is from Reg to V1 to V2 to V3 to FTD\r\n",
          "* absolute funnel indicates to use the date of the level.\r\n",
          " - DateTime_Reg for reg\r\n",
          " - V1_Date for Verification Level 1\r\n",
          " - V2_Date for Verification Level 2\r\n",
          " - V3_Date for Verification Level 3\r\n",
          " - FTD_Date for FTD\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          " * fast funnel indicates that between each step a maximum of 7 days have passed\r\n",
